function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	--Play Ambient Convo
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(Frac_Glac_Cath_01, actorIosef)
	
	--Wait for Convo Finish
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_ACOLYTE_01, Frac_Glac_Cath_01)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_ACOLYTE_02, Frac_Glac_Cath_01)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(actorIosef, Frac_Glac_Cath_01)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorIosef)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorIosef)

	--Acolyte 1 move action
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_ACOLYTE_01, ID_LOC_ACOLYTE_01, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_ACOLYTE_01, 1)
		
	--Acolite 2 move action
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_ACOLYTE_02, ID_LOC_ACOLYTE_02, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_ACOLYTE_02, 1)

	--Refocus Ioseph + Addresses PC
	Hydra.ActorFaceActor(actorIosef, idActor)

	--Play Ambient Convo P2
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(Frac_Glac_Cath_01B, actorIosef)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(actorIosef, "MOVED")
	
end
